Ranger Help for: build shelter
================================

SYNTAX:      build
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to construct a camp shelter for resting in
the wilderness. The Ranger must have the necessary materials, including
rope and wood or other tent components. A shelter provides a safe place
to rest and recover. The quality of the shelter depends on the Ranger's
skill level and the materials available. Shelters are temporary and
will eventually deteriorate.
